{"tid":954514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一齊入黎倒數","createTime":"2018-12-24T16:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T17:14:48.000Z","uid":220068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5843525752c055296628e1b483aad9da67e35e","tid":954514,"uid":220068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"入得黎倒數 知咩事啦<br />\n上年好地地有個暖粒粒聖誕 今年lonely christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都講咗好耐既分手旺季（9~12月）唔通真係咁邪<br />\n特登有心要一班受害苦主聖誕過年冇人陪？<br />\n圍爐既就一齊圍吓啦 仲有5分鐘都講定 各位Merry Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝各位開開心心 開party有約有著落既可以一直keep住 要返工既就第日再慶祝過<br />\n冇約既好快就有約<br />\n除夕應該會再開多次倒數 各位無論過成點都好 連登有愛呀呀呀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454a436d25969148e7362bd45b3e9417087a5fc6","tid":954514,"uid":220068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"fail咗 兩秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a885b4896d50dfc585b26219868147b251ba507","tid":954514,"uid":188418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:14:48.000Z","msg":"7 days, 14 hours, 45 minutes, 34 seconds"}]}